y ibn Ka\u2019b reported: There was a man who lived the furthest from the mosque, as far as I know. He never missed a congregational prayer. It was said to him, \u201cIf you buy a donkey, you can ride it during the dark nights and hot days.\u201d The man said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/every-step-mosque-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":15891,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Every step to mosque for prayer is rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever purifies himself with ablution in his house, then he walks to a house among the houses of Allah to fulfill an obligation among the obligations of Allah, one step of his will expiate his sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14009,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/waiting-prayer-fortress\/","url_meta":{"origin":15891,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Masjid: Waiting for consecutive prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of a deed by which Allah expiates your sins and raises your status?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThorough ablution despite difficulty, taking many steps\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13560,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/dua-enter-exit-mosque\/","url_meta":{"origin":15891,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for entering, leaving Masjid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Usayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you enters the mosque, let him say: O Allah, open for me the doors of your mercy. When he leaves, let him say: O Allah, I ask you for your favor.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5824,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/02\/virtue-masjid-al-haram-nabawi\/","url_meta":{"origin":15891,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Virtue of praying at two sacred mosques","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Zubayr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in this mosque of mine is better than a thousand prayers in any other mosque, except the Sacred Mosque. Prayer in the Sacred Mosque is one hundred times better than prayer in this mosque\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"tex